  <prompt>spec.md Assumption flags this: user-to-sprk_organization mapping mechanism is not yet defined. Options per spec: (a) Dataverse N:N between systemuser and sprk_organization, (b) configurable lookup field. Pick + implement.</prompt>
  <goal>OrganizationMembershipResolver.GetOrganizationIdsAsync(systemUserId) returns set of GUIDs for organizations the user belongs to. Mechanism is documented + repeatable. Defaults gracefully when no mappings exist.</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec Assumption">Mechanism choice documented in task notes + ADR-034</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md §A">BFF pre-merge checklist</constraint>
  </constraints>
