  <steps>
    <step order="0">Context check + spec Assumption on sprk_organization mapping</step>
    <step order="1">Survey existing schema: does sprk_organization have a user lookup? Is there an existing N:N?</step>
    <step order="2">Decide mechanism (default to N:N if no existing mechanism); document decision in notes</step>
    <step order="3">If N:N: create relationship; if lookup: add field</step>
    <step order="4">Implement OrganizationMembershipResolver.GetOrganizationIdsAsync</step>
    <step order="5">Unit + integration tests with seeded fixture</step>
    <step order="6">Cross-reference decision in ADR-034 draft</step>
  </steps>
